STOCK DURING THAT PERIOD. DURING THE FOURTH QUARTER OF 2014, 59.9 MILLION SHARES WERE DELIVERED AND RETIRED UNDER THE ASR, AND THE FINAL NUMBER OF SHARES TO BE DELIVERED WILL BE DETERMINED AT THE CONCLUSION OF THE PURCHASE PERIOD.

