THE COMPANYS FISCAL YEAR IS THE 52 OR 53-WEEK PERIOD THAT ENDS ON THE LAST SATURDAY OF

SEPTEMBER. THE COMPANYS FISCAL YEARS 2014, 2013 AND 2012 ENDED ON SEPTEMBER 27, 2014, SEPTEMBER 28, 2013 AND SEPTEMBER 29, 2012, RESPECTIVELY. BOTH FISCAL YEARS 2014 AND 2013 SPANNED 52 WEEKS. FISCAL YEAR

2012 SPANNED 53 WEEKS, WITH A 14

TH

WEEK INCLUDED IN THE FIRST QUARTER OF 2012, AS IS DONE APPROXIMATELY EVERY SIX YEARS TO REALIGN THE COMPANYS FISCAL QUARTERS MORE CLOSELY TO CALENDAR

QUARTERS. INCLUSION OF THE ADDITIONAL WEEK IN 2012 INCREASED THE COMPANYS OVERALL NET SALES AND OPERATING EXPENSES FOR THE YEAR.

