NOTES INCLUDE THE INTEREST ON THE NOTES, AMORTIZATION OF THE DISCOUNT AND, IF APPLICABLE, ADJUSTMENTS RELATED TO HEDGING. THE COMPANY RECOGNIZED $381 MILLION AND $136 MILLION OF INTEREST EXPENSE ON ITS LONG-TERM DEBT FOR THE YEARS ENDED

